{
  "id": "adv_card_mei_06_02",
  "title": "早坂芽衣",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_living_noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "う～んいい匂いだな～\n見て見て、{user}さん",
      "startTime": 4.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "ケーキの土台は完璧な焼き上がりだよ！",
      "startTime": 7.1913149675,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "焼き上がりはいいんだけど……\n真ん中に穴が空いてるのはどうしてだ？",
      "startTime": 12.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "うん！\nドーナツみたいで美味しそうでしょ",
      "startTime": 16.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "ドーナツとケーキの組み合わせで\nダブルで美味しいの！",
      "startTime": 22.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "これぞ芽衣の発明した最強スイーツだよ！",
      "startTime": 24.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうか……俺はスイーツには詳しくないから\n芽衣に任せるよ",
      "startTime": 32.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "よ～し、次は飾り付けだよ\nイチゴはたっぷり使おっと！",
      "startTime": 38.0666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cooking-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4000,
          "startTime": 42.0666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cooking-03.m4a",
          "delay": 8600.000000000002,
          "startTime": 46.6666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cooking-03.m4a",
          "delay": 11233.333333299996,
          "startTime": 49.3
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "手早く進めよう。生クリームはグラニュー糖を\n入れてよくかき混ぜるのか……案外難しいな",
      "startTime": 43.9,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 15066.6666667,
          "startTime": 58.9666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 19033.3333333,
          "startTime": 62.9333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんの帰りは夕方だから、じっくり丁寧に\n……って、琴乃ちゃんからメッセージだ",
      "startTime": 59.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "えっと――芽衣、今、どこにいるの？\nクリスマスライブのことで聞きたいことがあるの",
      "startTime": 71.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "……だって。ねえ、{user}さん\n琴乃ちゃん、なんか気付いてるっぽくない？",
      "startTime": 79.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃は鋭いしな。これまでの芽衣やみんなの言動から\n何か感付いたのかもしれない",
      "startTime": 86.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "ど、どう返事したらいいかな？",
      "startTime": 89.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "普段通りの芽衣でいいと思う\n変に隠そうとすると、かえって怪しまれる",
      "startTime": 95.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "わ、分かった！　いつもの芽衣だね！\nえ、えっと……",
      "startTime": 101.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "――拝啓。師走の候、貴方様にますますのご繁栄の\nこととお慶び申し上げます。平素は格段の厚情を――",
      "startTime": 109.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "硬い、硬いって！　別人になってるから",
      "startTime": 115.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "ごめ～ん、もう送っちゃった\n琴乃ちゃん、凄く怪しんでるみたい",
      "startTime": 122.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "諦めるのはまだ早いぞ\nすぐ普段の芽衣らしい返信を送って、リカバーしよう",
      "startTime": 128.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei014.m4a",
      "text": "普段の芽衣ってどんな感じだっけ？\n分からなくなっちゃったよ～",
      "startTime": 136.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな……もっと親しげで、人懐っこくて\nまっすぐな女の子だよ、芽衣は",
      "startTime": 143.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei015.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、そうかな、照れちゃうな～",
      "startTime": 146.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "今は照れてる場合じゃない",
      "startTime": 151.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei016.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったね、ごめん。えっと、琴乃ちゃん、お疲れ～\n今はね、{user}さんと一緒だよ、っと",
      "startTime": 161.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "俺と一緒なのは、書かない方がいいんじゃないか？\nサプライズの件に気付かれるかもしれない",
      "startTime": 169.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei017.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、そっか。失敗失敗\n芽衣、なんでも正直に話しちゃうから",
      "startTime": 175.8666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3599.9999999999945,
          "startTime": 179.4666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8566.666666599986,
          "startTime": 184.4333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei018.m4a",
      "text": "って、琴乃ちゃんから返信だ！　早いな～\n{user}さんとどこで何してるの、だって",
      "startTime": 185.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "単独の仕事のことで、事務所で打ち合わせしてる\n……って伝えるんだ",
      "startTime": 194.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei019.m4a",
      "text": "うん、分かった。単独の仕事のことで……\n…………う～ん",
      "startTime": 203.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei020.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣、琴乃ちゃんに嘘つきたくないな\n友達だもん",
      "startTime": 209.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "……芽衣らしいな。でも、寮でバースデーケーキを\n作ってるって、正直に伝える訳にもいかないだろ",
      "startTime": 215.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei021.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんだけど……\nなんとか嘘つかずに内緒に出来ないかな？",
      "startTime": 222.6666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3599.9999999999945,
          "startTime": 226.2666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei022.m4a",
      "text": "……あっ、琴乃ちゃんからまたメッセージだ\n芽衣の返信が遅いから、気にしてるみたい",
      "startTime": 230.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei023.m4a",
      "text": "どうしよう、{user}さん、助けて～",
      "startTime": 234.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、寮にいることだけ伝えよう。後は何も\n心配はしなくていいって。これなら嘘じゃないだろう？",
      "startTime": 242.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
