      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃の執念を感じるな……。なんだって？",
      "startTime": 266.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei026.m4a",
      "text": "――良かった。ちょうど、私も忘れ物を取りに\n寮に向かってるから、会って話したい――だって",
      "startTime": 275.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "ここに来るのか？　マズいぞ！\n調理を中止して、ケーキと材料を隠さないと",
      "startTime": 283.7333333334,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9099.999999899977,
          "startTime": 292.8333333333
        }
